---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Terms of Service" description="Lock & Logic terms of service — booking policies, rules, liability, and conditions of use.">
  <PageHero title="Terms of Service" subtitle="Last updated: February 2026" />

  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="space-y-8 text-sm leading-relaxed text-steel-200">
        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>By accessing our website or using our services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our website or services.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">2. Booking & Payment</h2>
          <p>All bookings are made through our online reservation system. Payment is required at the time of booking. Prices are per person and include the full escape room experience, pre-game briefing, and post-game debrief. We accept major credit cards and digital gift cards.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">3. Cancellation & Refund Policy</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">We understand plans change. Our cancellation policy is as follows:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-steel-400">
            <li><strong class="text-steel-200">24+ hours before:</strong> Full refund or free reschedule</li>
            <li><strong class="text-steel-200">Less than 24 hours:</strong> No refund, but we'll do our best to reschedule</li>
            <li><strong class="text-steel-200">No-shows:</strong> No refund or reschedule</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">4. Assumption of Risk & Liability</h2>
          <p>Escape room activities involve moving around enclosed spaces, solving physical puzzles, and operating in low-light environments. By participating, you acknowledge these inherent risks and agree that Lock & Logic is not liable for any injuries, damages, or losses incurred during your visit, except where caused by our negligence. All participants must sign a waiver before playing.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">5. Rules of Play</h2>
          <p class="mb-3">To ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for everyone:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc space-y-1 pl-5 text-steel-400">
            <li>No excessive force — if it doesn't open easily, it's not meant to be opened that way</li>
            <li>No climbing on furniture, fixtures, or set pieces</li>
            <li>No food, drinks, or gum in the rooms</li>
            <li>No cell phones — they must be stored in the provided lockers</li>
            <li>Participants must not be under the influence of alcohol or drugs</li>
            <li>Follow all Game Master instructions</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3">Violation of these rules may result in removal from the room without a refund.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">6. Age Requirements</h2>
          <p>Players under 16 must be accompanied by a participating adult (18+). Players aged 16–17 may play without an adult present but must have a waiver signed by a parent or legal guardian.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">7. Photo & Video Policy</h2>
          <p>We may take photos or record video in common areas and during post-game celebrations for promotional purposes. By visiting our facility, you consent to the use of your likeness in marketing materials. If you prefer not to be photographed, please inform our staff upon arrival.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">8. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>All puzzles, room designs, narratives, branding, and website content are the intellectual property of Lock & Logic. You may not reproduce, distribute, or disclose puzzle solutions or room details without our written consent.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to update these terms at any time. Continued use of our services after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the revised terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="mb-3 font-heading text-xl font-bold text-steel-100">10. Contact</h2>
          <p>For questions about these terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@lockandlogic.com" class="text-gold-400 transition-colors hover:text-gold-300">info@lockandlogic.com</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
